enchantment.mccoursemod.auto_smelt.desc: When applied on pickaxe transform all items that can be roasted on furnace.
enchantment.mccoursemod.block_fly.desc: When applied on pickaxe if player has flying speed mining equals if player has on ground.
enchantment.mccoursemod.glowing_mobs.des: When applied on helmet armor all entities are detected with X-Ray of mobs. (Press M key to activated or disabled)
enchantment.mccoursemod.immortal.desc: When applied to tools, armor, etc., it prevents the loss of the item in cactus, TNT, lava, void, etc.
enchantment.mccoursemod.lightning_strike: When applied on sword when player hits on entities appears lightning, but player receive damage if attacked.
enchantment.mccoursemod.lightstring.desc: When applied on bow increases bow loading speed.
enchantment.mccoursemod.magnet.desc: When applied on pickaxe all mined blocks automatically store on Player's inventory.
enchantment.mccoursemod.magnetism.desc: When applied on leggings armor searches for items and Experience Orbs on the ground within a radius and returns them to the Player's inventory.
enchantment.mccoursemod.more_ores.desc: When applied on pickaxe if a stone block is break has a percentage to receive ores.
enchantment.mccoursemod.peaceful_mobs.de: When applied on leggings armor all entities not attack Player.
enchantment.mccoursemod.rainbow.desc: When applied on pickaxe the broken ore is replaced and turned on an ore block.
enchantment.minecraft.aqua_affinity.desc: When applied on helmet armor increases underwater mining speed.
enchantment.minecraft.bane_of_arthropods: When applied on sword or axe increases damage to arthropod mobs also Spiders, Bees, Silverfish, Endermites, etc.
enchantment.minecraft.binding_curse.desc: When applied on armor the player not remove the item of inventory.
enchantment.minecraft.blast_protection.d: When applied on armor add bonus damage reduction of explosions and fireworks.
enchantment.minecraft.breach.desc: When applied on mace ignores 15% of armor damage reduction per level.
enchantment.minecraft.channeling.desc: When applied on trident produces lightning when thrown at a mob or lightning rod while a thunderstorm is occurring.
enchantment.minecraft.density.desc: When applied on mace increases 0.5 additional damage per level for each block fallen with tool.
enchantment.minecraft.depth_strider.desc: When applied on boots armor increases underwater movement speed.
enchantment.minecraft.efficiency.desc: When applied on axe, pickaxe, shovel or hoe increases mining speed.
enchantment.minecraft.feather_falling.de: When applied on boots armor reduces fall damage the player takes, but it does not affect falling speed.
enchantment.minecraft.fire_aspect.desc: When applied on sword or axe an entity received fire attack when hit.
enchantment.minecraft.fire_protection.de: When applied on armor add bonus damage reduction of fire.
enchantment.minecraft.flame.desc: When applied on bow shoots flaming arrows.
enchantment.minecraft.fortune.desc: When applied on axe, pickaxe, shovel or hoe receives bonus loot drops of ores.
enchantment.minecraft.frost_walker.desc: When applied on boots armor creates frosted ice blocks when walking over water, and causes the wearer to be immune to damage from certain blocks such as campfires and magma blocks when stepped on, but not working with lava.
enchantment.minecraft.impaling.desc: When applied on trident deal extra damage on each hit against aquatic mobs also axolotls, dolphins, guardians, squid, turtles, all variants of fish, etc. Except drowned is an undead mob.
enchantment.minecraft.infinity.desc: When applied on bow one arrow is needed to used the enchantment that prevents regular arrows from being consumed when slot.
enchantment.minecraft.knockback.desc: When applied on sword or axe increases knockback distance of entities.
enchantment.minecraft.looting.desc: When applied on sword or axe increases amount of drop loot of entities.
enchantment.minecraft.loyalty.desc: When applied on trident causing it to return to the owner once thrown.
enchantment.minecraft.luck_of_the_sea.de: When applied on fishing rod increases luck while fishing to received enchantments, armors, tools, etc.
enchantment.minecraft.lure.desc: When applied on fishing rod decreases the wait time for a bite on the hook.
enchantment.minecraft.mending.desc: When applied on tools or armor regenerates tools, equipments, etc. only player received XP.
enchantment.minecraft.multishot.desc: When applied on crossbow shoot three arrows or firework rockets at the cost of one.
enchantment.minecraft.piercing.desc: When applied on crossbow causes arrows to pierce through entities.
enchantment.minecraft.power.desc: When applied on bow increases arrow damage.
enchantment.minecraft.projectile_protect: When applied on armor add bonus damage reduction of projectiles.
enchantment.minecraft.protection.desc: When applied on armor add bonus damage reduction.
enchantment.minecraft.punch.desc: When applied on bow increases an arrow's knockback, but it not affect damage dealt of arrows.
enchantment.minecraft.quick_charge.desc: When applied on crossbow quickly reloading a crossbow.
enchantment.minecraft.respiration.desc: When applied on helmet armor extending breathing time underwater.
enchantment.minecraft.riptide.desc: When applied on trident hurls the user in the direction the user is facing, but only when they are wet.
enchantment.minecraft.sharpness.desc: When applied on sword or axe increases melee damage attack on entities.
enchantment.minecraft.silk_touch.desc: When applied on axe, pickaxe, shovel or hoe receives the broken block.
enchantment.minecraft.smite.desc: When applied on sword or axe increases damage dealt to undead mobs also Skeleton, Zombie, Wither, Phantom, Zoglin, etc.
enchantment.minecraft.soul_speed.desc: When applied on boots armor walk more quickly on soul sand and soul soil blocks.
enchantment.minecraft.sweeping.desc: When applied on sword or axe increases sweep attack damage on entities.
enchantment.minecraft.sweeping_edge.desc: When applied on sword or axe increases sweep attack damage on entities.
enchantment.minecraft.swift_sneak.desc: When applied on leggings armor walk more quickly while sneaking.
enchantment.minecraft.thorns.desc: When applied on armor if entities attacked player receives damage.
enchantment.minecraft.unbreaking.desc: When applied on tools or armor increases durability of tools, equipments, etc.
enchantment.minecraft.vanishing_curse.de: When applied on tool or armor if player killed the item disappears of inventory.
enchantment.minecraft.wind_burst.desc: When applied on mace the player into the air seven blocks per level after performing a smash attack.
